@NODE IMOB "Imagine Objects"

vh5150.lha    	Guitar based on Eddie Van Halens famous red,black and white
		stripey design. The pattern is applied with coloured faces
		rather than brush mapping. Has a tremelo arm etc.

SportCar.lha	Imaginary prototype sports car.

FightPln.lha	Imaginary prototype jet fighter aircraft, unusual because
		it's a biplane.

Daleks.lha	The worst enemies of Dr Who. The object is mainly black,
		and is grouped so that the moving parts can be animated.
		There are two versions in the archive, which use faceted
		and non faceted spheres. These require 2.5M and 5M memory
		respectively to scanline render.

FaceMask.lha	Low resolution face shape. Ideal for use as tribal mask.

sonic.lha	S*nic the Hedgehog object. Yes the star of many a video
		game comes to your favourite rendering package!

lemming.lha	Simple version of the cute characters from the Psygnosis
		games. Cycle object which can be animated.

DinoVr.lha	Dinosaur object based on a velociraptor. Uses Imagine 3.0
		textures. The object size is 550K and requires quite a bit
		of RAM to render!

@ENDNODE 

